     <text:p text:style-name="P20"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc1023_1230340041" office:name="Between My Ears I Cannot Sing" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">Between My Ears I Cannot Sing<text:tab/>18</text:a></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P20"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc1317_3007704144" office:name="Never Bad News" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">Never Bad News<text:tab/>20</text:a></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P20"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc1123_1230340041" office:name="Ollie If He Was A Chinese Eunuch" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">Ollie If He Was A Chinese Eunuch<text:tab/>21</text:a></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P20"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc1315_3007704144" office:name="As I Lay Here Beside You" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">As I Lay Here Beside You<text:tab/>22</text:a></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P20"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc1313_3007704144" office:name="Clouds" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">Clouds<text:tab/>23</text:a></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P20"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc1125_1230340041" office:name="Instagramification I – No Time And Nothing To Do" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">Instagramification I – No Time And Nothing To Do<text:tab/>24</text:a></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P20"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc1125_1230340041%20Copy%201" office:name="Instagramification II – A Classic" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">Instagramification II – A Classic<text:tab/>25</text:a></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P20"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc1969_4086586558" office:name="Nothing Hurts" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">Nothing Hurts<text:tab/>26</text:a></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P20"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc776_3676532460" office:name="Goodbye Ollie," text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">Goodbye Ollie,<text:tab/>29</text:a></text:p>
    </text:index-body>
   </text:table-of-content>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P22"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P23"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1293_3676532460"/>Preface<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1293_3676532460"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P24"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P25"><text:span text:style-name="T6">The sum total of this book amounts to nothing but a joke. I refuse to stop telling this joke all on the grounds that I find it funny. I’ve lately been stopping myself, because I think it’s in bad taste now that Ollie’s escaped me. I’ve reached my bounds. A book I reread recently captures what I hope to present through this collection</text:span>:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P26"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Quote">All of the true things I am about to tell you are shameless lies.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Quote"><text:span text:style-name="T7">—</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T8">Kurt Vonnegut, Jr., </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cat’s Cradle</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P27"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P28">Nothing in these pages are true. Everything I’ve written comes from my heart and what I believe to be somewhat funny, or a little interesting. That probably means there’s something true in here, but that’s not up to me to decide.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P29"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P30">Otherwise, all writing was formed with a single thought in mind: “How do I make Ollie a little uncomfortable here, but still willing to laugh about it?” If I hit the mark, you’ll know. <text:span text:style-name="T9">If not, forgive me— Nothing was meant too serious to cause harm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">And yes, I use the em-dash: NO AI was used throughout </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T11">this collection</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T6">As a final </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T12">note on why I did this</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T12">t</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T13">here’s </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T14">nothing</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T13"> wrong with wanting to be an individual. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">The only thing wrong is to </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T12">not </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">try.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P33"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T6">So that’s what I hope to get across here: I’m trying. I tried. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T12">If I failed, better than those that never pursued a thought to its end.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P33"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">Thank you.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P36"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37">I aint ever felt better and</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37">I aint ever been dumbe<text:span text:style-name="T1">r.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:span text:style-name="T15">—</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T16">Jesse Welles</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P39"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P40">To give anything less than your best</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P40">is to sacrifice the gift.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P41">—<text:span text:style-name="T17">Steve Prefontaine</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P42"><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis">I can’t even guess myself what it must be</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P42"><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis">to live the life of a human being.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T18">—</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T19">Osamu Dazai, </text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T20">No Longer Human</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T20"/></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P43">See the cat?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P44"><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T21">See the cradle?</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P44"><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T18">—Kurt Vonnegut, Jr., </text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T21">Cat’s Cradle</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T19"/></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P45"><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T22">I don’t want to be normal,</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P45"><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T22">I want to be me</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P45"><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T19">—</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Emphasis"><text:span text:style-name="T23">My Brain</text:span></text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P46" loext:marker-style-name="T24"><text:span text:style-name="T24"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P47"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc155_3645116443"/><office:annotation office:name="__Annotation__441_2779579312" loext:resolved="false">
     <dc:creator>Vladimir Herdman</dc:creator>
     <dc:date>2026-05-09T23:32:14.079003000</dc:date>
     <meta:creator-initials>VTH</meta:creator-initials>
     <text:p text:style-name="Comment">I’m thinking overly positive from here, to goofy/weird, to whatever I want towards the end of the book here.</text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="Comment"/>
    </office:annotation>Hello Ollie<office:annotation-end office:name="__Annotation__441_2779579312"/>,<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc155_3645116443"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">Hello Ollie,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">From the first moment I met you I—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">When we met that fated August, I really wanted to just—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">Ollie, the effect you’ve had on me, truly...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">I just can’t start this letter to you. I feel I can’t speak my mind. I don’t have the words to express myself, and I keep <text:span text:style-name="T10">trying to rewrite everyting</text:span>. So, that’s what this book is for.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">I plan on expressing some emotions— or thoughts— at least somewhere within this piece, ideas I couldn’t fully write out, ideas I had to keep rewriting ‘till I finally gave up. <text:span text:style-name="T10">And yes, I use the emdash throughout.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">This book, and every poem, is an attempt <text:span text:style-name="T25">a</text:span>t <text:span text:style-name="T25">some</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T25">nebulous feeling within me</text:span>. Whether you call it poetry or not, that’s why the cover says this is a collection of “Maybe-Poems.” Got all my bases covered <text:span text:style-name="T10">here</text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">I hope you enjoy it! I hope it’s not too weird! I hope…</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">I hope you thought it was funny.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">Sincerely,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">Dare I say lovingly,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">I dare,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">I do dare,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P48">Vova</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49">Never Have I Ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50">Never have I ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50">gotten fucked up at a party. OH YEAH!.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50">Never have I ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50">broken someone’s table at a RAGER!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P51">Never have I ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P51">wanted to drink ‘till I PUKE!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P51">Never have I ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P51">wanted a hangover. UH huh.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50">Never have I ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50">ignored a phone call. <text:span text:style-name="T26">cool</text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P51">Never have I ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P51">stayed home to be alone.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P52">Never have I ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P52">made a mistake.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50">Never have I ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50">promised to change.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50">Never have I ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T26">hid</text:span> something <text:span text:style-name="T27">to fit in</text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50">Never have I ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50">regretted a decision.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P51">Never have I ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P51"><text:s text:c="2"/>felt like I wanted to speak to you</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P51"><text:s text:c="2"/>been the good one all alone</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P51"><text:s text:c="2"/>told you everything you mean to me</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P53"><text:s text:c="2"/><text:span text:style-name="T27">dreamt</text:span> of a face I should <text:span text:style-name="T27">forget</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P51"><text:s text:c="2"/><text:span text:style-name="T27">mean everything I say—</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P51"><text:s text:c="2"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50">Never have I ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P50"><text:span text:style-name="T27">missed</text:span> You <text:span text:style-name="T27">more</text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1331_3007704144"/><office:annotation office:name="__Annotation__1492_1230340041" loext:resolved="false">
     <dc:creator>Vladimir Herdman</dc:creator>
     <dc:date>2026-06-16T21:39:50.354253000</dc:date>
     <meta:creator-initials>VTH</meta:creator-initials>
     <text:p text:style-name="Comment">Make it a dick joke.</text:p>
    </office:annotation>Rising Action<office:annotation-end office:name="__Annotation__1492_1230340041"/><text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1331_3007704144"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P54"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P54"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P55"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1329_3007704144"/><office:annotation office:name="__Annotation__1467_1230340041" loext:resolved="false">
     <dc:creator>Vladimir Herdman</dc:creator>
     <dc:date>2026-06-16T21:39:14.486307000</dc:date>
     <meta:creator-initials>VTH</meta:creator-initials>
     <text:p text:style-name="Comment">Base off ‘She Was Brand’ by E. E. Cummins.</text:p>
