   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc820_3326894427"/>Soapstone<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc820_3326894427"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">My heart is one of those</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">smooth stones,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">hard to hold</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">and easy to drop—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">to drop hard.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">It’ll slip right through</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">your shaking fingers as you</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P62">squeeze to the rhythm</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P62"><text:span text:style-name="T30">and keep me alive</text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">My stone is like oil</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">and won’t mix</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">with your water,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">no matter how much</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">we hold on.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">I only make</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">myself clean</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">slipping through</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P64">your fingers.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc818_3326894427"/>Another Place, Another time<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc818_3326894427"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">Are you <text:span text:style-name="T31">waiting</text:span>,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">are you out there;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">Pushing off the now</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">and thinking of...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">Check back again</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">after I&apos;ve made it.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">When we meet, <text:s/>when I, <text:s text:c="3"/>when I,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">when I see you.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">There&apos;s tomorrow—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">always tomorrow.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">Promise.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1025_1230340041"/>I’m Not Struggling<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1025_1230340041"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">All the media I watch</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">portrays love as a struggle</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">of wills against some force,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">of conflict and resolution—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">a drama.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">The protagonists come together,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">and through their struggle</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">against some other force,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">learn to love eachother,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">strengthen their bonds,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">and form resolute declarations</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">of understanding about the other<text:span text:style-name="T32">s</text:span>,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">as can only be learnt from</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">facing hell with someone.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">I <text:span text:style-name="T32">f</text:span>eel in myself a desire</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">for <text:span text:style-name="T32">your</text:span> time, <text:span text:style-name="T32">but</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">I don&apos;t think it&apos;s love,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P65">I don’t think it’d last after the first date.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"><text:span text:style-name="T32">M</text:span>aybe that&apos;s the culture in me,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">based off what I consume.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">I&apos;ve broken my ability to love wholly,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">because I&apos;m incapable of loving</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">when times are good.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">I love when it&apos;s bad.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">I don&apos;t have many issues,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">and I&apos;m afraid to be</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"><text:soft-page-break/>incapable of love.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">Am I lonely,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">or forcing myself to...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">What do I like.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">I&apos;m disgusting.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">And I think I’m happy.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1319_3007704144"/>Maybe-Poem<text:span text:style-name="T33">s</text:span><text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1319_3007704144"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">Not enough image,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P67">and too <text:span text:style-name="T33">direct to</text:span> be a poem.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">I&apos;ve just written</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">and thrown in</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">some</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">random</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">line-breaks</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">here and</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">there;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">Maybe an expression</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">of something on my mind,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">but so far,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">there&apos;s no meter or prose</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">worth keeping on the page—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P68">or in my heart.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">But hey,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">Bukowski called them his</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66"><text:s text:c="4"/><text:span text:style-name="T34">hot beer shits</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T15">,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">and I don&apos;t feel that way</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">about anything here,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">so I think I&apos;ll call them</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66"><text:s text:c="4"/>maybe-poems,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P70">from a</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P70"><text:s text:c="4"/>maybe-person,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">or, maybe <text:s text:c="2"/>maybe</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">maybe a poem,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">a poem that</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">may be,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66"><text:soft-page-break/>if only a</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">person like me</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">may be</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">around</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">someone like</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66">You.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1023_1230340041"/>Between My Ears I Cannot Sing<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1023_1230340041"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P66"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">As you walked away</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P71"><text:tab/><text:span text:style-name="T35">I</text:span>t was my heart that first beat out of my chest. Slapping onto the floor, it kept pulsing while my teeth fell out and my skin sloughed off and my bones jumped out the hole in my chest, and the organs and liquids without their cage poured from me an ungodly spray of everything else wet and human.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P72"><text:tab/>All around, an ensemble started to their sections. The large intestine and colon formed chairs as small hand bones made stands for hairy sheet music. Muscle fibers rewrapped around jaw bone to fret strings, while the lungs, teeth, and larynx became a choir, and the skull a drum. Blood boiled, then congealed with lips and spit to form the brasses.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P72"><text:tab/>At the very center, a heart pumped erect as the conductor. Holding a metatarsal, it started waving <text:span text:style-name="T35">the</text:span> baton as the orchestra reared and let out every innermost</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P72">desire.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P72"><text:tab/>Used to furtive glances, eyes now drowned in your sight burnt onto skin. Ears listened for the first time to ideas that were never given a second chance, having always been caught at the back of a throat, which now sang with teeth secrets never shared about everything extraordinary, beautiful, and you. Fingers flexed for a missed touch, all the while drumming on the one that hid it all.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P72"><text:tab/>Each part played their misuse, but I could not command them to stop. Just a single organ left, I tried to <text:soft-page-break/>convey every fault I ever had, every reason to avoid m<text:span text:style-name="T35">e</text:span>— but nothing came out as familiar hands raised the conductor, and I realized how perfect everything would be if only it was</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">without me.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P73"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc780_3676532460"/>Be Normal<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc780_3676532460"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P74"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P74">I don’t want to be normal,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P74">I want to be me.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P74"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P74">Isn’t that enough?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1317_3007704144"/>Never Bad News<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1317_3007704144"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I must have been born wrong.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I think— <text:s text:c="2"/>I think—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I think there must be something</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">that separates me from everyone,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">that something went wrong</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">in my development,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">that something isn&apos;t normal in me.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P75">That somethin<text:span text:style-name="T36">g</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P75">makes me not like you.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I want—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I want to be like you,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I want to be normal,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">but something&apos;s wrong.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I don&apos;t know what happened,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">but somewhere along the line,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I got lost,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">and no one came back</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">to find me.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">No one ever</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">wants to bring</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">bad news.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49">So What If I’m Not Normal</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">Fuck being normal:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">I’ve never met a normal person</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">my whole life.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">From day one it’s been</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"><text:span text:style-name="T37">weird shit</text:span> that define<text:span text:style-name="T38">d</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">my every <text:span text:style-name="T38">remembered</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">experience with others.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">No one I’ve ever come across</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"><text:span text:style-name="T38">had</text:span> a <text:span text:style-name="T38">boring</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T37"> </text:span>life;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">everyone’s hiding something ‘till</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">they can share a little more of themselves,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">‘<text:span text:style-name="T38">till their bursting at the seams of</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P76">wanting to connect over</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">hobbies,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"><text:span text:style-name="T37">little interests</text:span>, or</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"><text:span text:style-name="T37">secrets</text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"><text:span text:style-name="T38">I</text:span>f I had to be</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">more like someone else,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">there’d be no point to the whole</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">of my life <text:span text:style-name="T39">being lived</text:span>. <text:span text:style-name="T37">So</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">I like me,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69">even if—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"><text:span text:style-name="T38">if</text:span>—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P69"><text:span text:style-name="T38">i</text:span>f You <text:span text:style-name="T40">didn’t</text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1123_1230340041"/>Ollie <text:span text:style-name="T41">If</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T41">H</text:span>e <text:span text:style-name="T41">W</text:span>as <text:span text:style-name="T41">A Chinese Eunuch</text:span><text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1123_1230340041"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I woke up last night,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">no dihh—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">Oh, uhhh</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">昨晚我醒过来,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">发现没屌了.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1315_3007704144"/>As I Lay Here Beside You<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1315_3007704144"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I can only stare at the back of your head,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">wondering</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">on what I should do,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">on how I should talk to you tomorrow.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">If I could but reach out</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">and touch you</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">as I can now laying here,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I would show you this heart—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">place your hand over my chest,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">this feeling made real.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">As I lay here beside you,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I don&apos;t want to wake up</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">to an empty bed</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">and remember</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">yesterday&apos;s</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">Dream.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1313_3007704144"/>Clouds<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1313_3007704144"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">I&apos;ve caught myself</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">looking out towards the horizon</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">at clouds, big ones—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">so sharp their silhouette—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">just staring.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">I wonder if</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">that is what mountains</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">look like</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">from far away.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">I just want to keep looking.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">I want to keep wondering if <text:s text:c="2"/>if <text:s text:c="6"/>if</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">what I see is what I&apos;ll get,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77"><text:span text:style-name="T42">if</text:span> there’s <text:span text:style-name="T42">so much more</text:span> out there.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">I want <text:s text:c="2"/>I want</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">I want to keep looking</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">at <text:span text:style-name="T43">those</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T43">distant</text:span> clouds</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77"><text:span text:style-name="T43">until </text:span>they disappear when</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P77">I <text:span text:style-name="T42">forget to stare</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T44">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1125_1230340041"/>Instagramification <text:span text:style-name="T45">I </text:span>– No Time And Nothing To Do<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1125_1230340041"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P78"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P78">I&apos;ve really got</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P78">nothing to do,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P78">and so little time</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P78">to do it.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P79"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1125_1230340041 Copy 1"/>Instagramification<text:span text:style-name="T45"> </text:span>– <text:span text:style-name="T46">A Classic</text:span><text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1125_1230340041 Copy 1"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Roses are red,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"><text:span text:style-name="T46">V</text:span>iolets are blue,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Ollie, my bed—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Just me and you.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1969_4086586558"/>Nothing Hurts<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1969_4086586558"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">When I wake up at night, I can’t move.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">I see it standing in the corner, like</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">it’s afraid of me: Mass of flesh</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">and a concave face, bent in</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">and hiding features.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">It drips in the</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">darkness.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">I</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">never</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">got to hate</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">you, because I</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">never got to know you.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">A chasm inside a torso and</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">where you should be— nothing.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">We are frozen as space shrinks.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">It’s forced closer, or I am. In</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">shadow without feature,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">it drips down into</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">cupped hands.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Finger gaps</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">spill.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Silent</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">car rides,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">and awkward</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">phone calls. Nothing said</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">over bad food or in company.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"><text:soft-page-break/>Something hurts in between the</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">moments, but all I can remember are</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">eyes, blue and piercing. Pink with</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">tears; made only sharper still.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">They drip onto me, and</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">search my features.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Frantically pore</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">over a face,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">lost.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">I don’t have your eyes.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Hands reach outward</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">and ruffle hair, grope</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">face, and pull <text:span text:style-name="T47">a</text:span> nose.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">It cracks my jaw and</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">raises a chin, searching.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Grip tighter the throat</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">as tears fall fatter;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">No features alike.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Beat on the chest</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">and caress downward,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">digging into stomach.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Rip through muscle</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">and gorge on blood,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">while scanning through</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">a blur for something</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">that was never there.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Pull out my entrails</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">like they belong to you,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">dragging past the abdomen,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">lower and lower with his</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"><text:soft-page-break/>hands gaunt and bruised—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">working hands—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">reaching farther underneath</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">until <text:s/>unt i l <text:s text:c="2"/>u n t i l—</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">a blanket is pulled higher.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Space returns, and we separate</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">from embarrassment. Look</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">as hands raise to cover</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">eyes, crying rivulets.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">We merge into</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">our shame,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">apart.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Once</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">was here,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">but now you’re</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">gone. I can’t lose</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">what I never knew,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">so what do I miss? Forget </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">it, as the twilight into the dusk.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">I’m awake. Light stabs through closed</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">blinds, and I can move freely.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">There’s paper in my hands,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">fingers white with grip.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">I can’t let go. What</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">haunts me.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P80">Nothing.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc776_3676532460"/>Goodbye Ollie,<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc776_3676532460"/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P81"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I feel utterly and irrefutably incapable of expressing myself fully within the bounds of the language I have grown up with. One of my greatest fears is that I am a wholly uni-faceted individual with no complex emotions and extreme predictability in my actions.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">Maybe I’m not all that afraid of being unable to express myself, but that there’s nothing to express. I’m afraid of being nothing, that I have no dramatic knots in my living cords.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">I’m sorry for making any of this. It was a waste of time, and I’ve only made myself sadder. I will one day be my undoing. Everything I say is a lie, and just a way to convince myself there’s something more to who I am. Forgive my reachings and idiosyncrasies for what they are, a lack of character and a desire for what I don’t have.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">Sincerely,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Poetry_20_Text">Vova</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P82">About the Author</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P83"/>
