    </draw:frame>Herdman is a <text:span text:style-name="T48">well-meaning </text:span>person from Northeast Ohio. At the time of publishing, he <text:span text:style-name="T49">is 21 years old and </text:span>has know<text:span text:style-name="T50">n</text:span> Oliver Hendricks for 3 years. <text:span text:style-name="T51">He may never write again.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P83"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P83">If you’ve gotten this far, you know enough about me.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P82">About the Muse</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P83"/>
